{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><em><code>onload</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend\"><code>onloadend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart\"><code>onloadstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> 混入（mixin）的 <strong><code>onload</code></strong> 属性是一个<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Event_handlers\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">事件处理程序 (en-US)</a>，用于处理 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;等元素的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"load\"><code>load</code></a> 事件。</p>\n<p><code>load</code> 事件在给定的资源加载完成时触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> functionRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>functionRef</code> 是窗口 <code>load</code> 事件触发时调用的处理函数。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomethingElse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onload test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES5\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load event detected!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES2015\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">load</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load event detected!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The load event fires when the document has finished loading!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"注意","title":"注意","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在文档加载完成后会触发&nbsp;<code>load</code>&nbsp;事件。此时，在文档中的所有对象都在 DOM 中，所有图片、脚本、链接以及子框都加载完成了。</p>\n<p>同时也会有 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Events\">DOM 事件</a>，如&nbsp;<code>DOMContentLoaded</code>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code>（它们可以使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a> 来处理），这些事件在页面 DOM 构建起来后就会触发，而不会等到其它的资源都加载完成。&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onload","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onload"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onload","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"load\"><code>load</code></a> 事件</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/DOMContentLoaded_event\" title=\"DOMContentLoaded\"><code>DOMContentLoaded</code></a>&nbsp;事件</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/IIFE\">立即调用函数表达式（IIFE）</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"注意","id":"注意"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"GlobalEventHandlers 混入（mixin）的 onload 属性是一个事件处理程序 (en-US)，用于处理 Window、XMLHttpRequest、<iframe> 和 <img> 等元素的 load 事件。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"windo